%% Device Driver Parameters
%C Device Driver Parameters
These tunable parameters are associated with Device Driver processing.
% NUMREGPT
Specifies the number of regular pseudo-terminal devices.
Changing this tunable parameter is not sufficient
to change the number of pseudo-terminal devices on your system;
you must reinstall the nsu package.
% NUMSCOPT
Specifies the number of SCO pseudo-terminal devices.
Changing this tunable parameter is not sufficient
to change the number of SCO pseudo-terminal devices on your system;
you must reinstall the acp package.
